<br>
By virtue of my race, I'm KOS in Feerrott and Ogguk.  No problems in Neriak, I can even train there, but for whatever reason aggro the undead guards outside the guilds there.  I can live with that.  My question is, as an Erudite SK serving Cazic, what would my KOS status be in Butcherblock and the evil outpost at The Overthere?  In most places, it is my class or deity that present the problem.  In BB I've heard that they don't attack trolls and ogres, so I could go to Crushbone if I skirt around Kelethin (although I think killing CB orcs hurts Neriak faction).  Could kill slaves there I suppose.  I know I'm still too low for most of OT, but hypothetically, would I be killed for being Erudite, or would my status be similar to in Neriak?  Dark Elves don't mind me -- Kizdean Gix?  Dragoon Zytl?  We're drinking buddies!  Dorn?  A great conversationalist!  But troll and ogre guards in their respective homelands scowl at me from across the swamp.<br>
<br>
Looking for some advice here, so that the Pink Plague can spread to new lands.<br>
<br>
<br>
Inver Chainheart, 38th Season Shaman<br>
Somberlain Wayfaerer, 38th Season Druid<br>
Co-Commander of the Justice Knights <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#112512><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/unephtu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nephtu</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#CCCCC8>(1/18/01 4:06:49 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Erudite SK faction</span><hr size=1> Your faction in the Overthere will be apprehensive, like all us evil types, and many agnostics. Don't kill Ogres in Timorous Deep, they're on VS faction. <br>
<br>
You will be KoS in Cabilis, but less so than most - it's a lot easier for Cazic types to work their Cabilis faction - a few hundred Sarnaks and goblins, plus a few thousand bone chips = welcome to Cabilis.<br>
<br>
I'm KoS to the Dorfs in Butcher Block as a Dark Elf/Innoruuk, I suspect you probably are too.   Troll &amp; Ogre faction is very hard to work, and probably not worth the effort.<br>
<br>
Yes, killing CB Orcs is mondo bad for Neriak faction.  Don't do it - the Dark Elves near Mistmoore are also on Neriak, so avoid them too.<br>
<br>
Be Evil!<br>
Nephtu Morgulduin<br>
Dark Elf SK, Crystal Oracle <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#112512><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/utremaile.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tremaile</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 160<br> <font color=#CCCCC8>(1/19/01 4:27:11 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Erudite SK faction</span><hr size=1> (This message was left blank) <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/utremaile.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tremaile</A> at: 1/19/01 4:27:48 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#112512><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/utremaile.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tremaile</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 161<br> <font color=#CCCCC8>(1/19/01 4:27:21 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Erudite SK faction</span><hr size=1> Outside of VS himself... who all is VS faction?<br>
