<br>
The Overthere (Evil Outpost &amp; Scorpikis)<br>
Timurous Deep (Ogres)<br>
Howling Stones aka Charasis (Just about everything)<br>
Karnors (Many creatures - Drolvargs &amp; some undead)<br>
Kaesora (Xalgoz &amp; crew, plus Spiders)<br>
<br>
You can hunt in Karnors &amp; Kaesora and not completely trash VS faction, if you're careful who you fight, and do the Berserker War braid quest a bunch o'times to make up for it.  Don't hunt in Howling Stones unless you're ready to trash VS permenantly. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#112512><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/utremaile.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tremaile</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 164<br> <font color=#CCCCC8>(1/20/01 6:56:24 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Venril's Buds</span><hr size=1> Welp, ogres in TD might be the reason why I can't get OT faction no matter how hard I try. hehehehe<br>
